Elle, it's OK. It's OK.

93
00:05:27,244 --> 00:05:29,330
It's OK. It's OK. It's OK.

94
00:05:34,668 --> 00:05:36,086
It's OK...

95
00:05:36,170 --> 00:05:38,422
It's OK. Look at me.

