00:05:42,843 --> 00:05:45,386
You can't push yourself that hard.
I've told you.

97
00:05:45,470 --> 00:05:46,679
I know.

98
00:05:47,972 --> 00:05:52,018
It's just that everybody else was...

99
00:05:52,393 --> 00:05:53,394
Playing?

